author: veithen
msg: Made the design of the message builders responsible for building SwA and MTOM messages a bit more object oriented by introducing a MIMEAwareBuilder extension interface. MIMEBuilder now essentially dispatches to an instance of that interface.
This allows us to use the proper Axiom API to build MTOM messages. It will also make it easier to implement AXIS2-5308.
